subject: LINKAGE CONSTRAINTS VIOLATED --  RESOLVED !!
msgSnippet: Thanks a lot to all members of this list !! There are no more linkage errors in my test application. Reding others messages, I had inserted the two lines in
messageBody:
Thanks a lot to all members of this list !!

There are no more linkage errors in my test application.

Reding others messages, I had inserted the two lines
in the excluded.properties , in Junit jar file:

exclude.6=org.w3c.dom.* and
exclude.7=org.xml.sax.*


And no more linkage errors happened.

Thanks a lot !!!

Romilson
